description:
Do you know what the good life is? Do you want it? In this sermon, Pastor Randy Skeete explains that Christ told us how we can have the good life when He spoke these words in Matthew 4:4: “It is written, Man shall not live by bread alone, but by every word that proceedeth out of the mouth of God.” Listen to this lecture to learn what “every word” really means, and how this Word provides the key to enjoying the good life that Christ offers us. When you start living by the Word of God you can start living the good life.

Discover more:
http://amazingdiscoveries.org
http://amazingdiscoveries.tv/media/1260/851-living-the-good-life/
